ty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of Deckers Outdoor Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/DECK\" title=\"Deckers Outdoor Corporation\">DECK</a></span>) are up 80% thus far in 2024 with the footwear maker setting multiple sales and earnings records this year.</p> <p>A large part of the momentum has been driven</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2157697910/image_2157697910.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742689-3-reasons-deckers-outdoor-stock-on-holiday-shopping-list", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:34:15"}, {"id": "4742688", "title": "Signify: Threats Still On The Horizon, But Will Inflect Eventually", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Blue LED lights.\" data-id=\"167155391\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1028px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/167155391/image_167155391.jpg?io=getty-c-w240