"description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Doughnuts\" data-id=\"155376667\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">pjohnson1/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Undercovered Dozen Introduction</h2> <p>The 'Undercovered' Dozen is a weekly Seeking Alpha editor-curated series highlighting 12 articles on lesser covered stocks from the previous seven days. We hope this provides ideas and inspires discussion among the community.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/155376667/image_155376667.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742666-undercovered-dozen-pagerduty-suss-microtek-high-tide-8x8-plus", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:10:37"}, {"id": "4742680", "title": "Salesforce: What 2024 Taught Us About Market Expectations", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Salesforce logo at its Corporate office in New York, NY, USA on August 18, 2022.\" data-id=\"1610021131\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">JHVEPhoto/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The sentiment around Salesforce's (NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRM#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRM#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\" target=\"_blank\">CRM</a>) stock always seems to be on the wrong side. </p> <p>Back in late 2020, the stock was trading at unsustainably high levels, while at the same time high GAAP profitability was still a distant dream. All that has resulted</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1610021131/image_1610021131.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742680-salesforce-what-2024-taught-us-about-market-expectations", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 21:03:40"}, {"id": "4742679", "title": "Rubrik Is Soaring, But It Is Time For Caution (Ratings Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medium shot looking through server rack of male IT professional working in data center\" data-id=\"1327443301\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Thomas Barwick</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><b>Rubrik, Inc.</b> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/RBRK\" title=\"Rubrik, Inc.\">RBRK</a></span>) stock was soaring on Friday after reporting stronger than expected earnings results. The cybersecurity company continues to post torrid top-line growth and delivered a \u201cbeat and raise\u201d quarter. After the huge run-up over the last several</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1327443301/image_1327443301.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742679-rubrik-is-soaring-but-it-is-time-for-caution-ratings-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:58:11"}, {"id": "4742692", "title": "Xtract One Technologies Inc. 2025 Q1 - Results - Earnings Call Presentation", "description": "<p>The following slide deck was published by Xtract One Technologies Inc. in conjunction with their 2025 Q1 earnings call.</p> <p><figure class=\"sa-presentation paywall-full-content invisible\" data-id=\"106072\"></figure></p>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742692-xtract-one-technologies-inc-2025-q1-results-earnings-call-presentation", "pub_date": "2024-12-06 20:50:05"}, {"id": "4742676", "title": "Victoria's Secret: Another Great Trade, Time To Play With House Money", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1287386736/image_1287386736.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Beautiful afro woman showing to be quiet\" data-id=\"1287386736\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" 